<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About North Glenmore Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
     <p class="par-lg">Bound by the Earl Grey Golf Club in the south, Lakeview Golf Course in the east, 50 Avenue SW on the north and the Crowchild Trail SW on the west, the community in North Glenmore Park offers plenty of green spaces that are ideal for refreshing morning or evening walks. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">North Glenmore Park homes for sale comprise of an eclectic mix of residential dwelling from single family detached units and rowhouses to condominiums and low-rise apartments. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">The low crime rates and proximity to multiple parks and golf clubs makes North Glenmore real estate a popular choice for young couples, growing families and retirees alike.</p>
        </div>
